doctype html
html
  head
    title About Us – Save Bytes
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="/about.css")
  body
    include index

    .about-hero
      h1 About Save Bytes

    .about-content
      .column
        p
          | Save Bytes is a platform dedicated to reducing food waste by connecting
          | restaurants with charities and community kitchens in need. Our mission
          | is to ensure that surplus food finds its way to those who need it most,
          | rather than ending up in landfills.
      .column
        h2 How It Works
        ul
          li Restaurants list available meals or ingredients.
          li Charities browse and claim donations in real time.
          li Once claimed, the charity picks up and distributes the food.
      .column
        h2 Our Vision
        p
          | We envision a world where no good food ever goes to waste,
          | and communities come together to fight hunger and protect the planet.

    footer.site-footer
      p © 2025 Save Bytes — All Rights Reserved